[src:miranda-language/pattern-matching] The computation may depend on the replaced portion of the scrutinee as well as on other bindings extracted from the scrutinee.
[src:miranda-language/pattern-matching] While some concepts are relatively common to many pattern languages, other pattern languages include unique or unusual extensions.
